\pard\tx283\tx566\tx1133\tx1700\tx2267\tx2834\tx3401\tx3968\tx4535\tx5102\tx5669\tx6236\tx6803\tx7370\tx7937\tx8503\pardeftab1102\li283\pardirnatural
\cf0 It\'92s important to understand this was not only a technological gap, but more so a process, workflow and human operations gap.\cf0  \
\
\cf0 The initiators identified inefficiencies, recurring problems and ultimately many opportunities for improvement in the space between development and operation. They understood that the closer the two seemingly disparate stages of a software product\'92s lifecycle are integrated, the quicker, leaner and simpler both sides become.\cf0  \
\
\cf0 Ultimately, their thinking and exploration led to a whole new branch of work, a whole new generation of tools and innovations such as continuous deployment or integration, as well as an unprecedented level of automation.\cf0  \
